	Moved low-level GCR functions to `gcr.c'.

Wed Apr 22 11:19:28 1998  Ettore Perazzoli  <ettore@comm2000.it>

	* Version 0.14.2.10.

	* true1541.c (true1541_read_disk_byte): Rotate disk correctly.

	* 6510core.c: Removed `TRUE1541_ROTATE' #ifdefs.
	* viad2.c: Likewise.
	* viad1.c: Likewise.

